data.description: Rare 5 bedroom walkout Ranch located in desirable Millard Oaks. This home has been beautifully updated and cared for. You'll appreciate the large eat in chefs kitchen that has been completely remodeled with soft close cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. You'll enjoy entertaining in the fully finished walk out basement.  Large fully fenced yard with sprinkler system. These are just a few of the amenities for this home! Schedule your private showing today!
